    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The complexity level of this function is considered medium due to the need to interpret overpunch characters, which involves understanding specific character mappings and applying conditional logic to convert these characters correctly."
        }
